Element.Documentation: Using this form you can set counters. Counters are looked up by the code.

Element.Caption: Current Position
Element.Documentation: Current position of the counter. When requesting the next position from the counter this number will be increased by a value set in the Increment field.

Element.Caption: User Name
Element.Documentation: Maps the internal user to the login user name.

Element.Caption: User Role
Element.Documentation: By assigning role to the user you give them permission to use the applicastion.

Element.Caption: Valid Until
Element.Documentation: Date until when the counter is valid. Only works if the counter is set to be evaluated by date.

Element.Caption: Created
Element.Documentation: Date and time of record creation

Element.Caption: Number Length
Element.Documentation: Number of digits. The resulting number will be padded by zeroes up to the number of digits set in this field.

Element.Caption: Id
Element.Documentation: Record Id. Primary key of the record.

Element.Caption: Manage Validity By Date
Element.Documentation: If set, counters are evaluated by date. This way you can e.g. restart counter every year.

Element.Caption: Contact
Element.Documentation: Owning business partner of the resource.

Element.Caption: From
Element.Documentation: Bottom limit of the counter. This is not the starting number.

Element.Caption: Name
Element.Documentation: Name of the authorization role. By this role the user will be authorized to access system functions (e.g. menu items).

Element.Caption: Created
Element.Documentation: Date/time when the record was created
Number by which counter numbers will be incremented.

Element.Caption: Updated By
Element.Documentation: User who updated the record last time.

Element.Caption: Code
Element.Documentation: Counter code that is typically hardcoded in the application or set in settings. By this code the counter is looked up.

Element.Caption: Updated
Element.Documentation: Date and time of the last record update.

Element.Caption: Updated
Element.Documentation: Date and time when the record was last updated

Element.Caption: Record Created (Server)
Element.Documentation: Date and time when the record was created (server)
Data BLOB - contains the actual attachment

Element.Caption: Valied From
Element.Documentation: Date from which the counter is valid. Only works when the counter is managed by date.

Element.Caption: Updated By
Element.Documentation: User who updated the record last time.

Element.Caption: To
Element.Documentation: Upper limit of the counter. After reaching this number the counter will raise errors when requesting new positions.

Element.Caption: Company Name 2 (First Name)
Element.Documentation: Company: Name line 2 Person: First Name

Element.Caption: Short Name
Element.Documentation: Short code used for quick searching.
